ActUnited Nations Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the United Nations Sudan Regulations
PrecisRegulations amending the THE UNITED NATIONS SUDAN REGULATIONS in order to (1) fulfill Canada's international legal obligation to implement the binding decisions of the Security Council set out in Resolution 2035 (2012), and (2) address miscellaneous amendments requested by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
